{"id": "v3_manufacturing_qc_symmetry_control", "instruction": "请给出该工序的控制措施。", "input": "对象:键槽对称度超差工序。", "output": "控制：校核装夹基准、提高分度精度、首件验证、刚性装夹\n关联因素：材料、几何、工艺参数、设备状态综合作用,避免单一归因。\n边界：键槽对称度超差的具体参数与判定需结合工艺规范与质量等级核定,无来源依据不引用标准编号。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "manufacturing_qc", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["manufacturing_process", "missing_information"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_manufacturing_qc_symmetry_control", "category": "manufacturing_qc", "sub_category": "mfg_symmetry", "evidence": ["键槽对称度超差"], "conditions": ["材料", "几何", "工艺参数", "质量要求"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_fault_diagnosis_gearbox_probe", "instruction": "请给出排查步骤。", "input": "设备现象:减速机振动温升油变质。", "output": "排查：油液分析磨粒、振动频谱找轴承/齿轮特征频率、查对中\n注意：区分根因与诱因,需证据闭环,区分需停机检查与可在线监测。\n边界：结论须以监测数据为证据;不得把可能原因写成唯一故障结论;处置结合具体型号与运行参数。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "fault_diagnosis", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["vibration_resonance", "wear_contact_fatigue", "inspection_ndt", "missing_information"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_fault_diagnosis_gearbox_probe", "category": "fault_diagnosis", "sub_category": "fault_gearbox", "evidence": ["减速机振动温升油变质"], "conditions": ["运行参数", "型号", "历史记录", "监测数据"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_material_heat_treatment_selection_高温工况", "instruction": "请说明该材料/热处理问题的要点与适用条件。", "input": "主题:高强度高韧性选材;工况:高温工况。", "output": "要点：中碳调质钢调质获强韧匹配;更高要求用表面淬火或渗碳钢。须同时看屈服、冲击、疲劳与淬透性,不只看抗拉强度。截面越大越需选淬透性高的钢。\n在高温工况下,性能与失效模式可能不同,须针对性评估。\n边界：高强度高韧性选材的具体性能与工艺参数需依材料牌号、热处理状态与标准确定,硬度以材料认证数据为准。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "material_heat_treatment", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["heat_treatment", "static_strength", "missing_information"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_material_heat_treatment_selection_高温", "category": "material_heat_treatment", "sub_category": "mat_selection", "evidence": ["要点：中碳调质钢调质获强韧匹"], "conditions": ["材料牌号", "热处理状态", "截面尺寸", "高温工况"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_material_heat_treatment_selection_腐蚀工况", "instruction": "请说明该材料/热处理问题的要点与适用条件。", "input": "主题:高强度高韧性选材;工况:腐蚀工况。", "output": "要点：中碳调质钢调质获强韧匹配;更高要求用表面淬火或渗碳钢。须同时看屈服、冲击、疲劳与淬透性,不只看抗拉强度。截面越大越需选淬透性高的钢。\n在腐蚀工况下,性能与失效模式可能不同,须针对性评估。\n边界：高强度高韧性选材的具体性能与工艺参数需依材料牌号、热处理状态与标准确定,硬度以材料认证数据为准。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "material_heat_treatment", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["heat_treatment", "static_strength", "missing_information"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_material_heat_treatment_selection_腐蚀", "category": "material_heat_treatment", "sub_category": "mat_selection", "evidence": ["要点：中碳调质钢调质获强韧匹"], "conditions": ["材料牌号", "热处理状态", "截面尺寸", "腐蚀工况"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_material_heat_treatment_tempering_高温工况", "instruction": "请说明该材料/热处理问题的要点与适用条件。", "input": "主题:回火工艺;工况:高温工况。", "output": "要点：回火温度决定强度与韧性权衡。低温回火保硬度,高温回火提韧性(调质)。须避开回火脆性区。具体工艺依材料牌号与性能要求。\n在高温工况下,性能与失效模式可能不同,须针对性评估。\n边界：回火工艺的具体性能与工艺参数需依材料牌号、热处理状态与标准确定,硬度以材料认证数据为准。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "material_heat_treatment", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["heat_treatment", "missing_information"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_material_heat_treatment_tempering_高温", "category": "material_heat_treatment", "sub_category": "mat_tempering", "evidence": ["要点：回火温度决定强度与韧性"], "conditions": ["材料牌号", "热处理状态", "截面尺寸", "高温工况"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
