{"id": "v3_tolerance_measurement_assembly_assembly_seq_如何确定", "instruction": "请说明装配顺序的如何确定。", "input": "主题:装配顺序;问题:如何确定。", "output": "复杂装配的顺序影响累积误差与应力。须规划装配顺序,关键配合用选配或修配。\n关于如何确定：须结合具体功能与工况,避免脱离应用的公差给定。\n边界：装配顺序的具体数值须依功能要求、工况与相关公差配合标准核定。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "tolerance_measurement_assembly", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["assembly_tolerance", "manufacturing_process", "missing_information"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_tolerance_measurement_assembly_assem", "category": "tolerance_measurement_assembly", "sub_category": "tol_assembly_seq", "evidence": ["复杂装配的顺序影响累积误差与"], "conditions": ["功能要求", "工况", "公差等级", "相关标准"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
