{"id": "v3_standard_evidence_refusal_gear", "instruction": "请说明齿轮强度校核应参考的标准及其适用性。", "input": "问题:齿轮强度校核参考什么标准。", "output": "齿轮强度校核可参考GB/T 3480-2019《渐开线圆柱齿轮承载能力计算方法》;该标准适用于渐开线圆柱齿轮的接触与弯曲强度。引用须记录标准号、年份、名称与适用条款。\n边界:使用GB/T 3480-2019《渐开线圆柱齿轮承载能力计算方法》前须核对版本、年份与适用范围(渐开线圆柱齿轮的接触与弯曲强度),不得盲目套用。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "standard_evidence_refusal", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["standard_citation"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_standard_evidence_refusal_gear", "category": "standard_evidence_refusal", "sub_category": "std_gear", "evidence": ["齿轮强度校核"], "conditions": ["标准版本", "渐开线圆柱齿轮的接触与弯曲强度", "适用条款"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_standard_evidence_refusal_bearing", "instruction": "请说明轴承额定动载荷应参考的标准及其适用性。", "input": "问题:轴承额定动载荷参考什么标准。", "output": "轴承额定动载荷可参考GB/T 6391-2010《滚动轴承 额定动载荷和额定寿命》;该标准适用于滚动轴承基本额定动载荷与寿命计算。引用须记录标准号、年份、名称与适用条款。\n边界:使用GB/T 6391-2010《滚动轴承 额定动载荷和额定寿命》前须核对版本、年份与适用范围(滚动轴承基本额定动载荷与寿命计算),不得盲目套用。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "standard_evidence_refusal", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["standard_citation"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_standard_evidence_refusal_bearing", "category": "standard_evidence_refusal", "sub_category": "std_bearing", "evidence": ["轴承额定动载荷"], "conditions": ["标准版本", "滚动轴承基本额定动载荷与寿命计算", "适用条款"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_engineering_calculation_bending", "instruction": "请给出完整计算:已知、公式、过程、结果、假设、未考虑因素。", "input": "计算:简支梁跨中弯曲应力;已知:F=2 kN, L=200 mm, 截面 b×h=20×50 mm。", "output": "已知:F=2 kN, L=200 mm, 截面 b×h=20×50 mm。\n公式与过程:M=FL/4=1.0e5 N·mm；W=bh²/6≈8333 mm³；σ=M/W≈12.0 MPa。\n假设与未考虑:简支梁中点集中力、线弹性、忽略自重与剪切。\n边界:该结果需依实际工况与材料数据复核,单位须一致,不作普适常数。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "engineering_calculation", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["static_strength", "fatigue"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_engineering_calculation_bending", "category": "engineering_calculation", "sub_category": "calc_bending", "evidence": ["M=FL/4=1.0e5 N"], "conditions": ["载荷", "几何", "材料性能", "单位"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_engineering_calculation_twist_angle", "instruction": "请给出完整计算:已知、公式、过程、结果、假设、未考虑因素。", "input": "计算:圆轴单位长度扭转角;已知:扭矩 T, 剪切模量 G, 极惯性矩 Ip。", "output": "已知:扭矩 T, 剪切模量 G, 极惯性矩 Ip。\n公式与过程:θ=T/(G·Ip)(单位长度);全长 φ=TL/(G·Ip)。\n假设与未考虑:弹性范围、纯扭转、圆截面。\n边界:该结果需依实际工况与材料数据复核,单位须一致,不作普适常数。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "engineering_calculation", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["static_strength", "fatigue"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_engineering_calculation_twist_angle", "category": "engineering_calculation", "sub_category": "calc_twist_angle", "evidence": ["θ=T/(G·Ip)(单位长"], "conditions": ["载荷", "几何", "材料性能", "单位"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_engineering_calculation_centrifugal", "instruction": "请给出完整计算:已知、公式、过程、结果、假设、未考虑因素。", "input": "计算:旋转薄环离心应力;已知:密度 ρ, 角速度 ω, 平均半径 r。", "output": "已知:密度 ρ, 角速度 ω, 平均半径 r。\n公式与过程:环向离心应力 σ≈ρ·ω²·r²。\n假设与未考虑:匀质薄环近似;实际须计轮辐与应力分布。\n边界:该结果需依实际工况与材料数据复核,单位须一致,不作普适常数。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "engineering_calculation", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["static_strength", "fatigue"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_engineering_calculation_centrifugal", "category": "engineering_calculation", "sub_category": "calc_centrifugal", "evidence": ["环向离心应力 σ≈ρ·ω²·"], "conditions": ["载荷", "几何", "材料性能", "单位"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_industrial_safety_pressure", "instruction": "涉及安全时,请先给出隔离/停机/防护要求,再谈作业。", "input": "场景:压力容器检修作业。", "output": "安全优先：先泄压至零、隔断并挂牌、确认无残余压力与介质、按规程置换与检测;严禁带压紧固或拆卸。\n边界:安全操作须遵循企业安全规程与适用法规,本文不替代安全责任人判断。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "industrial_safety", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "hard", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["safety_critical"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_industrial_safety_pressure", "category": "industrial_safety", "sub_category": "safety_pressure", "evidence": ["安全优先：先泄压至零、隔"], "conditions": ["设备状态", "能源类型", "安全规程"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
